≈ÚµU<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";s:555:"Tara is a clinical psychologist who completed her Master of Clinical Psychology at Griffith University. She has experience working across community mental health, hospital and private practice settings with children, adolescents and adults. She works with clients with a variety of concerns including anxiety, depression, trauma, adjustment difficulties, eating issues, chronic pain, and behaviour problems. Tara has a particular passion for working with children and young people, and is an accredited provider of the Triple P Positive Parenting Program.";}